tly criticize her because of her dark skin.\", \"from\": 284, \"to\": 437, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 340, \"end\": 357, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Instagram Stories\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the athlete\", \"from\": 301, \"to\": 312}, {\"ngram\": \"several videos\", \"from\": 322, \"to\": 336}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 384, \"to\": 390}, {\"ngram\": \"her dark skin\", \"from\": 423, \"to\": 436}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's worth noting that black Americans tend to have porous curly hair, so in order to put it in a classic bun or ponytail, you have to straighten it beforehand.\", \"from\": 438, \"to\": 598, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"black Americans\", \"from\": 461, \"to\": 476}, {\"ngram\": \"porous curly hair\", \"from\": 490, \"to\": 507}, {\"ngram\": \"order\", \"from\": 515, \"to\": 520}, {\"ngram\": \"a classic bun\", \"from\": 534, \"to\": 547}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As Simone noted in her video message, at the time of the recording, she was sitting on a bus with no air conditioning and 35 degree heatwave, which significantly affects the condition of her hair.\", \"from\": 600, \"to\": 796, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Simone\", \"from\": 603, \"to\": 609}, {\"ngram\": \"her video message\", \"from\": 619, \"to\": 636}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 641, \"to\": 649}, {\"ngram\": \"the recording\", \"from\": 653, \"to\": 666}, {\"ngram\": \"a bus\", \"from\": 687, \"to\": 692}, {\"ngram\": \"no air conditioning\", \"from\": 698, \"to\": 717}, {\"ngram\": \"35 degree heatwave\", \"from\": 722, \"to\": 740}, {\"ngram\": \"the condition\", \"from\": 770, \"to\": 783}, {\"ngram\": \"her hair\", \"from\": 787, \"to\": 795}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Do not address me because of my hair.\", \"from\": 797, \"to\": 835, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my hair\", \"from\": 827, \"to\": 834}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was done, but there is no air conditioning in the bus, and it's like 90,000 degrees,\\\" the athlete addressed her followers.\", \"from\": 836, \"to\": 961, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no air conditioning\", \"from\": 862, \"to\": 881}, {\"ngram\": \"the bus\", \"from\": 885, \"to\": 892}, {\"ngram\": \"90,000 degrees\", \"from\": 908, \"to\": 922}, {\"ngram\": \"the athlete\", \"from\": 925, \"to\": 936}, {\"ngram\": \"her followers\", \"from\": 947, \"to\": 960}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She shamed those who criticized her and warned them not to comment on her hair anymore, \\\"The next time you want to comment on a black woman's hair, just do not.\\\"\", \"from\": 963, \"to\": 1124, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her hair\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1041}, {\"ngram\": \"a black woman's hair\", \"from\": 1089, \"to\": 1109}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On the eve of the 2024 Olympic Games, she toldEllemagazine that she has accepted her hair as it is naturally, so she no longer worries about random statements.\", \"from\": 1126, \"to\": 1285, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the eve\", \"from\": 1129, \"to\": 1136}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1140, \"to\": 1162}, {\"ngram\": \"her hair\", \"from\": 1207, \"to\": 1215}, {\"ngram\": \"random statements\", \"from\": 1267, \"to\": 1284}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I used to be worried that my hair would be considered unprofessional, but now it does not bother me anymore,\\\" the gymnast said, adding, \\\"I am finally learning to love my hair, the texture I have, and the styles I can do.\", \"from\": 1286, \"to\": 1507, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my hair\", \"from\": 1313, \"to\": 1320}, {\"ngram\": \"the gymnast\", \"from\": 1397, \"to\": 1408}, {\"ngram\": \"my hair\", \"from\": 1454, \"to\